-----------------------------------
             TOUTATIS
-----------------------------------

A small 32-bit operating system written
for learning purposes.

To create a floppy image using Toutatis bootloader use:
- make floppy

To create an iso image using GRUB use:
- make iso

To build and run the kernel as a floppy image with
Toutatis bootloader:
- make qemu or make q
- make bochs or make b

To build and run the kernel as an iso image using GRUB:
- make qemu_iso or make qg
- make bochs_iso or make bg
